OBC...

Finally...after several tries, several pullers and thousands of miles on a
backed off axlenut....I have finally succeeded in breaking loose a rear drum
frozen to the axle splines.

When you're doing those brakes...don't forget to grease them damn axle
splines before putting that drum back on!  Now I just need to find time to
complete this brake job .  Then drop the motor for a reseal and other
maintenance.

